Bato babale ba yambo bakufi na coronavirus COVID-19 na Pointe noire, na Congo-Brazzaville. 
 Ministre ya bokolongo Lydia Mikolo nde apesi sango yango. Kolanda maloba ma ye, bato tuku mibale na mibale nde bayebani kozwama na COVID-19 na Congo-Brazzaville sika oyo.
Eyebani malamu te soki baye bakufaki bazwaki bokono bwango libanda to kati na mboka.





 


Lire aussi :


Président ya kala ya Congo Yhombi Opango akufi na COVID-19 na France





 
Kasi moko na na bawei azalaki mokambi ya misala milandaka fraude mpe repression. Awutaki France na sanza ya février.
O'mokolo mwa eyenga mokonzi ya kala Congo-Brazzaville, Jaques Joaquim Yhombi Opango akufaki na coronavirus pene na Paris, na France.
Nzokande alanga nzembo Arulus Mabele ya Congo-Brazzaville, ye, nde akufaki na bokono bwango pene mikolo zomi mileki, na Paris, na France.